{"tid":421938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新iPhone】蘋果忠粉：一張蘋果實物股票比iPhone X更難求","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T16:15:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"284851c422f58876a7003ad6335e9b6d4aaefc75","tid":421938,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司忠實擁躉魏志豪，在他逾千項蘋果收藏品中，決不賣掉的卻是蘋果公司的實物股票，他認為其收藏價值遠高於股票面值，是「賣一張、少一張」，甚至比iPhone X更難求。<br />\n<br />\n大蘋果眾MACitizen會長魏志豪於1996年大學畢業時，買入蘋果公司一股股票，並持有至今。儘管那一股股票沒讓他「發大達」，但他視之為珍藏，決不沽出。魏志豪稱，<a href=\"http://當年他是在美國網站oneshare.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%96%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99oneshare.com&d=%2BdsC6E34029Fg2a%2B2CxznbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=c5092ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">當年他是在美國網站oneshare.com</a>（已結業）買入蘋果一股股票，連計裝裱與運費合共千多港元，「當年蘋果兵荒馬亂，Steve Jobs未上場，股價得十幾蚊美金。」<br />\n魏志豪指當年想留來紀念多過投資，自買入股票後，蘋果分別於2000年與2005年將股份一拆二，他亦因此獲發多兩張蘋果股票證書。不過，2014年6月蘋果再將股份1拆7，魏志豪則沒再獲發新股票證書，因公司2010年已轉為電子化交易。據悉，「蘋果教主」喬布斯獲發首張的蘋果公司實物股票證書，去年標價19.5萬美元（約152萬港元）拍售。<br />\n魏志豪作為蘋果公司小股東，每年也收到蘋果從美國寄出的股息支票，卻全部無法兌現，因當年他以英文名「Derek Ngai」買股票，其身份證則沒有加上英文名字，故多年來的股息他只是「有得睇、冇得拎」，只好將支票與其他收藏品一同儲起。魏志豪稱，期待iPhone X面世，但未必搶購新機，因新機定價近萬元頗貴，而且加入多項新技術，或留待發展成熟才換機。<br />\n記者：伍詠雯<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171002/57277794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171002%2F57277794&d=%2BdsC6E34029Fg2a%2B2CxznbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=d9444a41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171002%2F57277794&h=8012c75b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171002/57277794</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171001/large/1506841966_5cf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171001%2Flarge%2F1506841966_5cf1.jpg&h=c911904f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年以英文名「Derek Ngai」買股票，身份證則沒有加上英文名字，多年來蘋果公司派發股息只是「有得睇、冇得拎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171001/large/1506841982_2d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171001%2Flarge%2F1506841982_2d9e.jpg&h=7553d238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDerek視每樣Apple產品如珍藏。"},{"pid":"3014feb6c8d77f4121132c54a75020adf96b4439","tid":421938,"uid":19762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"係真愛嘅就一早去咗入境處改名啦"},{"pid":"04db286908214cbff6ceafc57c626b4e5f7bcd89","tid":421938,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"佢呢一股而家值幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e251d1c160914bafc258f548be35567fc3d0b9","tid":421938,"uid":236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢呢一股而家值幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家150幾蚊美金1股"},{"pid":"696d390a74f404695f888431faa32945fd5e9f8a","tid":421938,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢呢一股而家值幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家150幾蚊美金1股</blockquote><br />\n應該係150x14=2100"}]}